00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:54,839
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ja sjela lagano, idem ja sad, ne ne.

320
00:26:54,839 --> 00:26:59,319
[SPEAKER_00] Deset minuta sam ja oklijevala i Benjamin je bio oko mene.

321
00:26:59,319 --> 00:27:01,579
